nodes.text: A member of the Kubaz species worked as a triple agent for the Hutt Cartel sometime during the Great Galactic War and Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. The Kubaz provided the Hutt Cartel with information that he gathered while undercover in both the Republic and the Empire, allowing the Cartel to take advantage of the warring galactic powers.
The Kubaz triple agent was first mentioned in the Codex entry for Kubaz in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011, but the Kubaz's name and gender were not specified.
